'''Flesh Crawlers''' are medium level monsters found in the second level of the [[Stronghold of Security]]. They drop the [[bottom of sceptre]], one of four parts of the [[Skull sceptre]]. Flesh crawlers drop [[herb]]s often, and are frequently killed for their uncommon [[Ranarr weed|Ranarr]] drops.

